"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td>",
"        7 to 9&nbsp;&micro;g/mL",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        Gram-negative pneumonia or acute life-threatening gram-negative infection in a critically ill patient",
